Package cz.cuni.mff

package cz.cuni.mff
This package contains the main class App of the Similar Fashion Finder application. It is responsible for orchestrating the whole process of connecting to the MongoDB and H2 databases, extracting products from JSON files and uploading them to the MongoDB collection, downloading images from remote URLs and uploading them to the H2 database, setting up the image search API and configuring the Swagger UI.
